.subheader
  .page-label Get Started

.page-content
  %p Gauge is super simple to install. The section below will show you how to get Gauge working in 4 simple steps. We think it will take you 5 mins. Thatâ€™s how easy it is!
  .tabs
    %ul.tabs-header
      %li.tab1
        %a.active{:href => "#tab1"}
          %i.fa.fa-apple
          Macintosh  
      %li.tab2 
